# FitMirror project rules

## Git workflow (required)
After every coding task that changes project files:
1. Run git commands from repo root: `C:\Users\moham\Desktop\OutfitAI\OutiftAI`
2. `git add` only relevant project files (never `backend/.env` or secrets)
3. Commit with a clear message describing why
4. `git push origin main`

Do not skip push unless the user explicitly says not to push for that task, or push fails (report the error).

## Stack and structure
- Vanilla JS only; no React/Vue/npm
- MediaPipe from CDN; Gemini key only in `backend/.env`
- One responsibility per JS file; console.log at key steps
- Touch only files relevant to the task; ask before structural changes
